{"tid":1453668,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(勸世) 希望覺位勇武或者支持繼續勇武抗爭既人停一停，入黎聽下我講","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:09:20.000Z","uid":37326,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef2a949a127a3926565a698867be2368075c149","tid":1453668,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"我同你地咁多個人一樣，睇到琴晚811既黑警既所作所為感到極之憤怒<br />\n甚至成晚訓唔著<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一合埋眼就見到位手足俾狗按係地下成面都係血不停講對唔住<br />\n一合埋眼就見到絲打俾狗射爆眼</span></span><br />\n我係一個有血有肉有良知既人，見到呢D 畫面傷害我地年青人，個心真係痛到不能形容，甚至同好多人一樣出現仇恨，想即刻就衝落街搵隻狗殺撚左佢。<br />\n<br />\n但靜落黎後，我覺得以報復心態去繼續爭取我地既訴求似乎係行唔通，因為太多港豬中立撚<br />\n同埋仲有如果我地用勇武去做鳩D 死黑警，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一班維穩既傳媒就可以有一大堆既黑材料去寫衰我地既義士，更重要既係我地會失民心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家仲記唔記得運動爆發冇幾耐果陣，有一為手足係連儂隧道俾一個藍絲廢老連續打左13拳而選擇唔還手既片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M6lwOz5FPyM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM6lwOz5FPyM&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpP4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=7296615d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M6lwOz5FPyM</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢位義士當時係贏盡香港人既掌聲，所有人都會一齊指責呢個廢老打鳩人，而且佢仲好快已經俾法庭判左傷人罪</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實我覺得琴晚811 黑警既所作所為就係呢個廢老既無限放大版本，宜家記者朋友已經實際影底晒黑警既罪行</span></span>，我覺得我地應該要學下呢位巴打既做法，我地選擇唔還手，我地先係被壓既一群，世界既眼睛我相信仲係雪亮既!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地應該要捉住黑警既罪項，無極限推廣文宣，將佢地點樣對香港既平民話俾全世界既人聽!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我明白大家好憤怒好嬲，好想為義士報仇，但諗清楚，再有更多既人被捕甚至受傷係唔係對得住義士既做法?? 我相信義士最想見到既係我地互相除低口罩擁抱果一下!<br />\n<br />\n唔岩聽既可以屌鳩我，可以負皮我<br />\n最後我都係想講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核爆都唔割</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3c0c5a92f22cacefc4631503d27ed8626b578837","tid":1453668,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8a6f8db242e6d911fb16ca3a32e18faae933c8d","tid":1453668,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1e79fb522a60a8fcf7a5578f828d55bf118d3c6","tid":1453668,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1a3d839bf9a8f9826a58105aee1722b2772b3ed","tid":1453668,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41c8f16d9892a3f76dae9a7efc5fdfe677a25a1b","tid":1453668,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:57:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"352e76d8743cabb30ae354da9f28be41a57b2abd","tid":1453668,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:57:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcfd23ad43ede0deadd0014d8d79521a5d57f04c","tid":1453668,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab68b0069f6ca99ed20bc434250ec9f6663b6339","tid":1453668,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850de062b945b7441585f9e30952c75654972107","tid":1453668,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig